I just got back from New Orleans from a kick ass concert it was EISLEY,REGGIE AND THE FULL EFFECT and NEW FOUND GLORY. If you get a chance to see EISLEY in concert go they will be at the Parish in the House of Blues in New Orleans on July 4.One of the biggest plus is they are one of the more personable band i ever met.They signed there cd, took pictures and talked to all the fans.I will be a fan because of that forever. New Found Glory was so good in concert the rocked the house. Reggie and the Full Effect was also awsome in concert

ciao 
scott

Hey i got back from new york this past weekend.I went to new york for two reasons. one was it was wrestlemania weekend and two it was my birthday. The whole weekend was a blast. I went to the beauty and the beast play on friday night. I meet even stevens star christy carlson romamo after the play.We walked around times square seeing everything we could. Meet a whole bunch of wrestlers. We got on tv monday night on WWE RAW. I finally got to talk to my girlfriend because the hotel had horrible reception any time she called i couldn't here her. that had me happier to talk to her. on the way home i got stuck at the airport because it was snowing. that is about it
